rComments: Great Prof and Great Guy - Very down to Earth unlike other professors in the department. His lectures and examinations focus on theory and the application of theories. His lectures are interesting and funny. You can attain more content and info from his 30 slide lectures than other profs 170 slide lectures.
He's absolutely hilarious!!! Easy to reach by email, very kind. :)

Never thought a great prof like him existed. Extremely nice, buys the entire class doughnuts on occasions. Teaches you the concepts, and tests you on them fairly. Office hours are very useful and productive. He is very clear on what he wants to test you on, and how you can prepare. He doesn't focus entirely on details, its all about understanding.
